widgets_values: This is an elegant gold-colored charm featuring a delicate, eye-catching design. The top section is shaped like a smooth, polished heart with a small crystal embedded near the top, adding a subtle sparkle. Attached to the heart is a dangling openwork floral design, resembling an intricate, layered flower or rose. The flower is adorned with numerous small, shimmering crystals evenly placed along its outline, giving it a luxurious and radiant appearance.
